videos.headline: Flau'jae Johnson denies Hawai'i from the 3-point line
videos.description: Flau'jae Johnson comes up with a nice block to prevent Hawai'i from shooting the trey.

videos.headline: Angel Reese powers her way in for 2
videos.description: Angel Reese swings by a pair of defenders underneath the rim and lays in the basket.

videos.headline: Angel Reese scores 34 as LSU cruises past Hawai'i
videos.description: Angel Reese goes 34-15-2 to help the LSU Tigers advance to face the Michigan Wolverines.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Angel Reese scores 34 as LSU cruises past Hawai'i) 2023/03/17 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: LSU's Reese dominates Rainbow Wahine in first round
videos.description: In the Tigers' 73-50 rout of Hawai'i, Angel Reese becomes the first SEC player this century with at least 30 points and 15 boards in a NCAA women's tourney game.
